Linear Discriminant Analysis

library(ISLR)
library(MASS)
smarket = Smarket

lda.fit=lda(Direction~Lag1+Lag2,data=smarket,
            subset=(Year<2005))
lda.fit

smarket = Smarket

qda.fit=qda(Direction~Lag1+Lag2,data=smarket,
            subset=(Year<2005))
